{"tid":326803,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"博帝(Patriot)稱其下RAM可完美運行Ryzen","createTime":"2017-07-18T09:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T23:34:00.000Z","uid":81059,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2afecec0f204387485416106935dc1e0891f8b0","tid":326803,"uid":81059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:29:57.000Z","msg":"AMD Ryzen平台發布後有很長一段時間面臨內存兼容性問題，尤其是多條經常無法上高頻率，不過隨著AMD、主板和內存廠商的不斷完善，這一問題已經逐漸不是事兒。<br />\n<br />\n今天，博帝(Patriot)也宣布，旗下的Viper 4、Viper Elite、Signature Line系列DDR4內存已經全線兼容AMD Ryzen AM4平台。<br />\n<br />\n博帝這個名字國內用戶可能不是太熟悉，不過要知道，AMD前幾年推出的自主品牌內存，其實就是用了博帝的條子，可見AMD對其品質的認可，而且至今都在銷售，只不過暫時看不到更新的跡象。<br />\n<br />\n按照博帝的說法，從單通道到四通道，從4GB到64GB，從2133MHz到3400MHz，其內存已經全線針對AMD Ryzen做了兼容性優化，可以保證穩定運行。<br />\n<br />\n測試所用主板如下：技嘉GA-AX370 Gaming K5、GA-AX370 Gaming K7、MSI X370 XPOWER GAMING TITANIUM、X370 SLI PLUS、A320M GAMING PRO，華碩ROG Crosshair VI Hero、PRIME B350-PLUS，華擎X370 Tachi、X370 Killer SLI 、AB350M Pro4、Fatali1ty AB350 Gaming K4、AB350M-HDV、A320M Pro4、A320M-HDV。"},{"pid":"69b7a67f57303169c5c3572e38bd35e5e1080f54","tid":326803,"uid":81059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:31:25.000Z","msg":"已經買左RAM既爸打們<br />\n有咩感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8c74ba6e24e67f0dcd244b48ca0af0269a0293","tid":326803,"uid":7758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:22:53.000Z","msg":"Ram support list有冇佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61dd97fdfb8fb024b688279fc0469c890a8ac998","tid":326803,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經買左RAM既爸打們<br />\n有咩感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇asus prime x370 pro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 其實唔太關事，喺prime x370上唔到3200嘅ram，可以喺msi x370穩上3200 @1.36v，相信似底板用料同bios問題多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c97b4f7ef0100e19bc5943245516f051e76177","tid":326803,"uid":40903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:04:56.000Z","msg":"最多咪換 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c14d2790d5a547b83793b363e7f196c38672e7","tid":326803,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:12:51.000Z","msg":"真係有白老鼠試左先講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9988850f695d221552c35fbc6992a9d5e37dfe67","tid":326803,"uid":13686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:04:02.000Z","msg":"Ram體質好超唔等於老母板超到上去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3414277d6769dd361d79c5b11d945a97e010549","tid":326803,"uid":37064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T05:44:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee5daa3529d3e352a839e31ae0e0cf2f03f2f135","tid":326803,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ram體質好超唔等於老母板超到上去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，呢方面我深有體會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087badac07585601e9c08344206bc8d3c57771d2","tid":326803,"uid":45393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:25:05.000Z","msg":"有貨既話一定係買galax hof"},{"pid":"0bb7c46ba0ab359f1fee8201eacce0b2524414ef","tid":326803,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:09:35.000Z","msg":"係咪真係行到 3000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c66255f995300e8593456996edc5b378a278f6d","tid":326803,"uid":40903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT